            <div class="title">
                Germany (Soviet Note)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1950-11-13/debates/41d94170-50e5-4602-bb82-51b41240fcb4/ParliamentaryPapers(Distribution)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
