    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-fd5dc406-1b5e-4847-bcec-861856fc8e0c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-fd5dc406-1b5e-4847-bcec-861856fc8e0c">
                Mr. Bevin
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-fd5dc406-1b5e-4847-bcec-861856fc8e0c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-11-13/debates/822688c5-84ab-4453-b545-c082ac25fca5/Germany(SovietNote)#contribution-fd5dc406-1b5e-4847-bcec-861856fc8e0c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Certainly. I have repeatedly stated in this House that when a conference is held it must be held on the old basis of the differences that exist and not limited to just one programme drawn up by Russia.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-fd5dc406-1b5e-4847-bcec-861856fc8e0c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-11-13/debates/822688c5-84ab-4453-b545-c082ac25fca5/Germany(SovietNote)#contribution-fd5dc406-1b5e-4847-bcec-861856fc8e0c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
